    <div class="red-header">LEAVE AGAINST MEDICAL ADVICE (LAMA/DAMA)</div>
    
    <div style="border:2px solid #cc0000; padding:15px; margin-top:20px; font-size:11px;">
        <h3 style="color:#cc0000; text-align:center; text-decoration:underline;">DECLARATION BY PATIENT / RELATIVE</h3>
        
        I, __________________________________ (Name), S/o / W/o __________________________________, 
        am the Patient / Relative of Patient __________________________________ (UHID: __________).
        <br><br>
        1. I have been explained in detail about the patient's medical condition and the need for continued hospitalization and treatment.
        <br><br>
        2. I have been explained the <strong>RISKS</strong> of leaving the hospital at this stage, which may include deterioration of condition, complications, permanent disability, or even <strong>DEATH</strong>.
        <br><br>
        3. Despite this medical advice, I am taking the patient out of Sewa Sadan Hospital on my own request and responsibility.
        <br><br>
        4. I hereby <strong>RELEASE</strong> the hospital, its doctors, and staff from any liability or responsibility for any consequences, including death, that may arise from this decision.
        <br><br>
        5. I have received the Discharge Summary and pending reports (if any).
        
        <br><br>
        <span style="font-family:'Mangal', sans-serif;">
        <strong>घोषणा:</strong> मुझे मरीज की गंभीर हालत और इलाज की जरूरत के बारे में समझाया गया है। मुझे बताया गया है कि अस्पताल छोड़ने से मरीज की जान को खतरा हो सकता है। मैं अपनी मर्जी और जिम्मेदारी पर मरीज को ले जा रहा हूँ। किसी भी अनहोनी या मृत्यु के लिए अस्पताल जिम्मेदार नहीं होगा।
        </span>
    </div>

